svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><div class=\"relative group\"><a class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/80 hover:text-electric-blue transition-colors flex items-center gap-1 uppercase tracking-wider\" href=\"/portfolio\">Company<svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"14\" height=\"14\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-chevron-down transition-transform duration-200\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m6 9 6 6 6-6\"></path></svg></a></div><a class=\"bg-electric-blue text-white px-6 py-2 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-wider hover:bg-electric-blue-lt transition-colors rounded-sm\" href=\"/contact\">Get Started</a></div><button class=\"lg:hidden text-white\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"28\" height=\"28\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></nav><main class=\"flex-grow\"><div class=\"pt-24 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 z-0 pointer-events-none opacity-50\"><div style=\"position:relative;width:100%;height:100%;overflow:hidden;pointer-events:auto\"><div style=\"width:100%;height:100%\"><canvas style=\"display:block\"></canvas></div></div></div><section class=\"relative py-24 md:py-32 overflow-hidden border-b border-white/5\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 bg-radial-[at_50%_0%] from-electric-blue/10 via-transparent to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 bg-midnight-mid border border-white/10 rounded-full mb-8\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-code-xml text-electric-blue\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"m18 16 4-4-4-4\"></path><path d=\"m6 8-4 4 4 4\"></path><path d=\"m14.5 4-5 16\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] font-bold text-grey\">Custom Software Development Nigeria</span></div><h1 class=\"text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold text-white mb-8 tracking-tighter leading-tight max-w-4xl mx-auto\">Bespoke Platforms for Nigerian Workflows</h1><p class=\"text-grey text-lg md:text-xl max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12 leading-relaxed\">Off-the-shelf software wasn&#x27;t built for your business. We build bespoke platforms — ERPs, SaaS products, internal tools — designed exactly for your Nigerian workflow.</p><div class=\"flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-12 pt-8 border-t border-white/10\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-mono\">30+</div><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey\">Platforms Built</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-mono\">100%</div><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey\">Code Ownership</div></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-1 font-mono\">95%</div><div class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-widest text-grey\">Client Retention</div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 bg-midnight-mid\"><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6\"><div class=\"mb-16 \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><span class=\"w-8 h-[1px] bg-electric-blue\"></span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-electric-blue font-bold\">The Challenge</span></div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Stop Settling for Weak Results</h2><p class=\"text-grey text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Many Nigerian businesses struggle to gain traction online due to outdated strategies and poor execution. Recognize these bottlenecks?</p></div><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-1 bg-white/5 border border-white/5\"><div class=\"bg-midnight p-8 hover:bg-midnight-lt transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">Spreadsheet Chaos</h3><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Running critical operations on spreadsheets leads to data entry errors, nothing syncing, and an inability to scale.</p></div><div class=\"bg-midnight p-8 hover:bg-midnight-lt transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">Bespoke Doesn&#x27;t Fit</h3><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Generic business platforms don&#x27;t handle your unique Nigerian workflow, tax calculations, or reporting needs.</p></div><div class=\"bg-midnight p-8 hover:bg-midnight-lt transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">Disconnected Systems</h3><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">Sales, inventory, accounting, and HR live in separate tools. No integration means constant manual data transfer.</p></div><div class=\"bg-midnight p-8 hover:bg-midnight-lt transition-colors\"><h3 class=\"text-white font-bold mb-4 tracking-tight\">Zero Customization</h3><p class=\"text-grey text-sm leading-relaxed\">You&#x27;re stuck waiting for someone else&#x27;s roadmap to get the features your business urgently needs.</p></div></div></div></section><section class=\"py-32 border-y border-white/5 relative overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-full h-full bg-radial-[at_50%_50%] from-electric-blue/5 to-transparent pointer-events-none\"></div><div class=\"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 relative z-10\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-20 items-center\"><div><div class=\"mb-16 \"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4 \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateX(-20px)\"><span class=\"w-8 h-[1px] bg-electric-blue\"></span><span class=\"text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] text-electric-blue font-bold\">Our Approach</span></div><h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight leading-tight\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">Strategy Built for the Local Market</h2><p class=\"text-grey text-lg max-w-2xl leading-relaxed \" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(20px)\">We don&#x27;t do generic. Our methodology is refined for the unique behavior of Nigerian consumers and the local competitive landscape.</p></div><ul class=\"space-y-6 mt-12\"><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start group\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-electric-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed\">Deep discovery sessions to map workflows and identify automation opportunities</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start group\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-electric-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed\">Technical architecture design with scalability and security built in</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start group\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-electric-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed\">Agile development with bi-weekly demo cycles for continuous feedback</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start group\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-electric-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed\">Rigorous testing including load testing and security audits</span></li><li class=\"flex gap-4 items-start group\"><div class=\"mt-1 text-electric-blue group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-circle-check\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"10\"></circle><path d=\"m9 12 2 2 4-4\"></path></svg></div><span class=\"text-grey text-lg leading-relaxed\">Deployment with full documentation, source code handover, and training</span></li></ul></div><div class=\"glass p-12 lg:p-16\"><h3 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-8\">What You Get</h3><div class=\"space-y-10\"><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">💻</span><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold tracking-tight\">Custom Platforms</h4></div><ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pl-12\"><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->SaaS Product Development</li><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->Internal HR/Inventory Tools</li><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->School &amp; EdTech Software</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">🔗</span><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold tracking-tight\">APIs &amp; Integrations</h4></div><ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pl-12\"><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->Fintech &amp; KYC Platforms</li><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->RESTful APIs &amp; Webhooks</li><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->Legacy System Integration</li></ul></div><div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-3xl\">📦</span><h4 class=\"text-white font-bold tracking-tight\">Handover</h4></div><ul class=\"grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-3 pl-12\"><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-1 h-1 bg-electric-blue rounded-full\"></span> <!-- -->100% Source Code Ownership</li><li class=\"text-grey text-xs flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"